01:49:08,590 --> 01:49:10,860
生命中只有两种悲剧
There are only two tragedies in life.

1408
01:49:11,360 --> 01:49:15,030
得不到你要的，跟得到你要的
One is not getting what you want. The other is getting it.

1409
01:49:15,270 --> 01:49:16,100
这是你卖的吗？
ls this one of yours?

1410
01:49:16,340 --> 01:49:19,170
