致命武器交付监管
Fake end-user certificates.

1417
01:49:46,770 --> 01:49:49,260
伪造使用者证明、虚设行号
Cut-out companies, meticulously catalogued.

1418
01:49:50,000 --> 01:49:52,700
世界各地军阀、独裁者…
There is hardly a warlord, dictator, despot anywhere in the world

1419
01:49:52,940 --> 01:49:56,300
暴君，无不跟你称兄道弟
that you're a first-name basis with.

1420
01:49:56,810 --> 01:50:01,750
你视为战利品的太太泄底的
It was your wife your trophy wife that led us to the prize.

1421
01:50:02,650 --> 01:50:05,780
不是她的错，她比较好跟踪
It's not her fault. She's just easier to follow than you are.

1422
01:50:07,650 --> 01:50:08,680
我可以看吗？
May l?

1423
01:50:09,320 --> 01:50:10,520
请便
Yeah, go ahead.

1424
01:50:35,550 --> 01:50:36,780
慢慢享用
Enjoy it.

1425
01:50:37,650 --> 01:50:39,380
- 什么  - 这个
- What?  - This.

1426
01:50:40,220 --> 01:50:42,240
我是你所有厌恶事物的化身
Tell me I'm everything you despise.

1427
01:50:42,720 --> 01:50:44,660
邪恶的代言人
That I'm the personification of evil.

1428
01:50:45,120 --> 01:50:46,530
我应该为社会组织和…
What?

1429
01:50:46,530 --> 01:50:51,190
世界秩序崩溃负责
responsible for the breakdown of the fabric of society and world order.

1430
01:50:51,400 --> 01:50:53,590
我是种族灭绝的幕后推手
I'm a one-man genocide.

1431
01:50:54,030 --> 01:50:55,970
想说什么现在都说出来
Say everything you want to say to me now.

1432
01:50:56,900 --> 01:50:58,390
因为你的时间不多
Because you don't have long.

1433
01:50:58,940 --> 01:51:03,840
你是清醒的，还是在妄想？
Are you paying attention? or are you delusional?

1434
01:51:03,940 --> 01:51:07,400
你破坏所有武器禁运条约
You have broken every arms embargo written.

1435
01:51:07,650 --> 01:51:08,980
你的罪证…
There is enough here to

1436
01:51:09,210 --> 01:51:11,770
足以判下好几个无期徒刑
put you away for consecutive life sentences.

1437
01:51:12,020 --> 01:51:13,790
在正式入狱服刑前…
You are going to spend the next ten years of your life

1438
01:51:13,790 --> 01:51:18,780
光跑法院就得耗上十年
going from a cell to a courtroom before you even start serving your time.

1439
01:51:21,390 --> 01:51:25,720
我想你还不了解你的处境
I don't think you fully appreciate the seriousness... ...of your situation.

1440
01:51:35,770 --> 01:51:38,300
我的家人不要我
My family has disowned me.

1441
01:51:40,150 --> 01:51:42,910
我太太和儿子抛弃我
My wife and son have left me.

1442
01:51:45,820 --> 01:51:47,480
我弟弟死了
My brother's dead.

1443
01:51:48,350 --> 01:51:49,960
相信我，我完全了解…
Trust me.

1444
01:51:49,960 --> 01:51:53,550
我的处境有多危险
I fully appreciate the seriousness of my situation.

1445
01:51:53,790 --> 01:51:55,190
但我向你保证…
But I promise you,

1446
01:51:55,960 --> 01:51:58,560
我不会花一秒钟在法庭
I won't spend a single second in a courtroom.

1447
01:51:59,830 --> 01:52:01,260
你在妄想
You are delusional.

1448
01:52:02,030 --> 01:52:03,690
我也不喜欢你，杰克
I like you, Jack.

1449
01:52:04,470 --> 01:52:08,130
或许喜欢，但我了解你
Well, maybe not, but I understand you.

1450
01:52:11,710 --> 01:52:13,700
我跟你说会发生什么事
Let me tell you what's gonna happen.

1451
01:52:14,910 --> 01:52:17,710
让你好及早做准备
This way, you can prepare yourself.

1452
01:52:21,890 --> 01:52:22,820
好吧
Okay.

1453
01:52:23,220 --> 01:52:26,520
很快会有人来敲门叫你出去
Soon there's going to be a knock on that door and you will be called outside.

1454
01:52:26,760 --> 01:52:29,060
大厅有个比你高阶的人
ln the hall there will be a man who outranks you.

1455
01:52:29,290 --> 01:52:32,290
首先他会恭维你立了大功…
First, he'll compliment you on the fine job you've done

1456
01:52:32,530 --> 01:52:34,660
世界因为你变得更安全
that you're making the world a safer place

1457
01:52:34,900 --> 01:52:38,560
你将获得表扬与升迁
that you're to receive a commendation and a promotion.

1458
01:52:39,370 --> 01:52:42,070
接着他说我会被释放
And then he'll tell you that I am to be released.

1459
01:52:42,310 --> 01:52:43,710
你抗议
You're gonna protest.

1460
01:52:44,740 --> 01:52:47,210
可能还威胁要辞职
You'll probably threaten to resign.

1461
01:52:47,680 --> 01:52:50,340
但最后我还是会被释放
But in the end, I will be released.

1462
01:52:50,880 --> 01:52:53,180
我被释放的理由跟你认为…
The reason I'll be released is the same reason you think...

1463
01:52:53,420 --> 01:52:54,910
我会被定罪的理由一样
I'll be convicted.

1464
01:52:55,490 --> 01:52:57,350
我的确跟一些…
I do rub shoulders with some of the most vile,

1465
01:52:57,590 --> 01:53:01,490
邪恶残暴的当代领袖称兄道弟
sadistic men calling themselves leaders today.

1466
01:53:02,830 --> 01:53:09,060
但其中有些人是我们敌人的敌人
But some of those men are the enemies of your enemies.

1467
