当你的老板是世界最大军火商
And while the biggest arms dealer in the world is your boss...

1468
01:53:14,310 --> 01:53:16,300
美国总统
...the President of the United States,

1469
01:53:16,540 --> 01:53:20,610
他一天运输的比我一年还多
Who ships more merchandise in a day I do in a year...

1470
01:53:21,180 --> 01:53:25,340
有时候在枪上留指纹很难堪
sometimes it's embarrassing to have his fingerprints on the guns.

1471
01:53:25,850 --> 01:53:28,750
有时候他需要我这种跑单帮的
Sometimes he needs a freelancer like me

1472
01:53:28,990 --> 01:53:30,090
送一些他不方便出面的货
to supply forces

1473
01:53:30,090 --> 01:53:38,360
所以，尽管说我邪恶
he can't be seen supplying. So... you call me evil,

1474
01:53:38,530 --> 01:53:43,060
但不幸，我是必要之恶
but unfortunately for you, I'm a necessary evil.

1475
01:53:59,320 --> 01:54:01,220
我想叫你下地狱…
I would tell you to go to hell.

1476
01:54:02,850 --> 01:54:04,820
但你已经在地狱里了
but I think you're already there.

1477
01:54:39,720 --> 01:54:41,490
很高兴跟你交易
Pleasure doing business with you.

1478
01:54:41,930 --> 01:54:44,290
多数人能出狱都很高兴
Most people are happy just to get out of jail.

1479
01:54:44,530 --> 01:54:48,230
我等人付钱请我出去，我不笨
I expect to be paid to leave. I'm not a fool.

1480
01:54:48,470 --> 01:54:50,020
今天他们需要我…
I know that just because they needed me that day

1481
01:54:50,270 --> 01:54:53,240
说不定下次我就变成代罪羔羊
didn't mean they wouldn't make me a scapegoat the next.

1482
01:54:53,470 --> 01:54:57,240
但我又回来重操旧业了
But I was back, doing what I do best.

1483
