你知道谁将坐拥地球？
You know who's going to inherit the Earth?

1486
01:55:22,430 --> 01:55:23,730
军火商
Arms dealers.

1487
01:55:24,100 --> 01:55:26,900
因为其他人都在战争中丧生
Because everyone else is too busy killing each other.

1488
01:55:27,510 --> 01:55:29,440
让我告诉你活命的秘诀
That's the secret to survival.

1489
